--auth
---- POST   /register {username, password, nickname, avatar} ✅
---- POST   /login    {username, password} ✅
---- DELETE /logout 🔐
--profile
---- GET  /
---- PUT  /avatar 🔐   {avatar}
---- PUT  /nickname 🔐 {nickname}
---- POST /follow 🔐 {username}
--tweets
---- GET  / (if not logged - return the tweets of the most popular user)
---- POST / 🔐 {text}
--comments
---- GET  /:tweet_id
---- POST / 🔐 {user_id, text, tweet_id}
--likes
---- POST / 🔐  {user_id, tweet_id}
